After a good run across the land, she neared the Maximal base again. 

Padding up to the valley, her optics watched the base carefully. She roared, 
calling out for someone to acknowledge her. Would be much easier have her old 
form with all her wicked gadgets. 

She stopped on the edge ofthe perimeter & waited.
